Drop ReShade `Shaders/` and `Textures/` directories here before publishing.

The standard pack is at https://github.com/crosire/reshade-shaders — the
"slim" branch is the smaller curated set:

    git clone -b slim --depth 1 https://github.com/crosire/reshade-shaders \
      /tmp/reshade-shaders
    cp -r /tmp/reshade-shaders/Shaders /tmp/reshade-shaders/Textures \
      ./reshade-shaders/

After populating, this .gitkeep file can be removed.

`ReShadePreset.ini` references SMAA, LumaSharpen, and AmbientLight by their
.fx filenames — those need to exist in `Shaders/` for the default preset to
load cleanly.
